{"word":"φατός","slug":"φατός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φατός</b></el> <el>(φᾰτός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:φημί'><el>φημί</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>that may be spoken</i>, <el>οὐ φατός</el> un- <i>speakable</i>, un- <i>utterable</i>, in- <i>effable</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>named, famous, notable</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}